Units
-----

1. Px (Pixel | picture element)
   size is fixed 

2. % percentage
   sets width according to device width 
   sets height according to its parent element

3. vh and vw 
   vh = viewport height 
   vw = viewport width 

   vh = 100% of device height
   vw = 100% of device width 

   1 vh = 1 % of device height
   5 vh = 5 % of 500px
        = 5/100 * 500
        = 25px

   1 vw = 1 % of device width
   5 vw = 5 % of 500px
        = 5/100 * 500
        = 25px